      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2021-10-27</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2022-10-06T15:07:26Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Emergency Relief for Servicemembers Act</strong></p> <p>This bill authorizes a servicemember to terminate specified contracts (e.g., contracts for commercial mobile service or internet service) that are entered into in relation to military orders for a permanent change of station if the member then receives a stop movement order in response to a local, national, or global emergency which prevents the member from using the services provided under the contract.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
